ests are more engaging at different times of the day\n- B. No, his mood and interests seem to change quite unpredictably\n- C. Sometimes he\'s more interested in an activity if it\'s presented in a certain way\n[step1: (Gathering information)]','complete','2024-02-01 13:26:02','gpt-3.5-turbo','a45c9fbf-a60d-4ba4-89da-463c0bab5e3f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('0075ad82-1feb-40a5-849b-3ac553c6b52e','660898a3963ff2eee1d3e680','6593bc7a65e63b8aec728732','tuwpfh','I\'m here to assist you with any challenging behavior your child might be exhibiting. Let\'s work together to find a solution.','delete','2024-03-30 22:58:42','gpt-3.5-turbo','7fa48b8f-32c7-4e5d-93cc-f7711f224771',NULL,NULL,NULL,'66088cb0963ff2eee1d3e67d'),('0092b2bb-f5e9-4a7b-8d70-d7c022ace27c','65bb7c88de44d1bc6d2badcc','6593bc7a65e63b8aec728732','A','Certainly! For the bedtime routine, start by choosing activities that are calming and enjoyable for your son. Consistency is key, so try to do the same things in the same order each night. For screen time, gradually reduce the intensity of the content as bedtime approaches, and eventually, aim to have no screens in the hour before bed. This can help his brain transition to a more relaxed state. How does that sound?\n- A. It sounds doable, I\'ll give it a try\n- B. I\'m a bit unsure, can you clarify?\n[step3: (discussion strategies)]','complete','2024-02-01 11:12:08','gpt-3.5-turbo','eed18cfa-f0c9-49af-87e8-219d3d17b3d9',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('009973c6-5126-487a-8658-d20b8401df19','65bbf797441f111009ff8536','6593bc7a65e63b8aec728732','B','Et comment réagit-il lorsqu\'il est dans sa chambre?\n- A. Il s\'excuse et se calme\n- B. Il continue à être en colère\n- C. Il sort de sa chambre sans permission\n[step1: (Gathering information)]','complete','2024-02-01 20:00:55','gpt-3.5-turbo','a45c9fbf-a60d-4ba4-89da-463c0bab5e3f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('009ca640-8e01-4900-991a-ee23729fee3c','65ba2548de44d1bc6d2bad36','6593bc7a65e63b8aec728732','B','Understanding the patterns can h